OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Fri 29 May to Sun 7 JunFThe
OL,6,Fsouth of the UK is expected to be
OL,7,Fmainly fine and dry at the start of
OL,8,Fthis period, with temperatures well
OL,9,Fabove normal. It will be cloudier in
OL,10,Fthe north with some rain at times,
OL,11,Fthis heavy in places. Moving into
OL,12,Fearly June, conditions will likely
OL,13,Fbecome unsettled across the UK as a
OL,14,Fwhole. Atlantic weather systems will
OL,15,Fmove in from the west bringing showers
OL,16,For longer spells of rain at times. The
OL,17,Frain will likely be heaviest in parts
OL,18,Fof the west and northwest.
OL,19,FTemperatures will probably be near
OL,20,Fnormal.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
