OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Mon 8 Jun to Mon 22 Jun
OL,6,FProbably changeable or unsettled at
OL,7,Ffirst with Atlantic frontal systems
OL,8,Fbringing showers or longer spells of
OL,9,Frain at times. From mid-month, high
OL,10,Fpressure may begin to become more
OL,11,Fdominant with conditions becoming dry
OL,12,Fand more settled, although some
OL,13,Fshowery interludes are still possible.
OL,14,FTemperatures are expected to be near
OL,15,Fnormal at first, but probably rising
OL,16,Fabove average later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
